# Ignore everything by default
*

# Except files with an extension (keeps .c, .h, .md, etc)
!*.*

# Except directories (so git can still look inside them)
!*/

# Specific folders to ignore (must come AFTER the rules above —
# the git rule is "last match wins", então listar antes não funcionaria)
.vscode
/TabelaVerdade

# Ignore Windows .exe binaries even though they have an extension
*.exe